looked at him that one time.

26
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,733
-[speaking japanese]

27
00:03:00,833 --> 00:03:05,266
-Hm, [repeats japanese],
my beloved husband.

28
00:03:05,366 --> 00:03:06,600
-[angry growl]

29
