00:03:16,966 --> 00:03:18,900
-Guess he forgot what
he was going to say.

35
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,441
Eh, Akane?

36
00:03:21,233 --> 00:03:22,433
-(NERVOUSLY) M-- m-- marry you?

37
00:03:22,533 --> 00:03:25,100
I mean, I can't because
I-- I-- you see-- I--

38
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,366
-[speaking japanese]

39
00:03:26,466 --> 00:03:31,533
-Hm, [repeats japanese], I
love you, it says, Akane.

40
00:03:31,633 --> 00:03:32,466
-Enough!

41
00:03:32,566 --> 00:03:33,007
OK?!

42
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,500
RANMA (VOICEOVER):
She's been trying

