time so I never noticed,

44
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:47,133
but Shampoo really
is kind of cute.

45
00:03:49,566 --> 00:03:52,933
Gee, if only Akane
were that nice.

46
00:03:53,033 --> 00:03:55,300
[groan]

47
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,600
-Ryoga, why'd you do that?

48
00:03:57,700 --> 00:04:01,500
-You know, watching Akane
get jealous over a jerk

49
