like you really makes me sick.

50
00:04:05,233 --> 00:04:05,674
-What?!

51
00:04:08,266 --> 00:04:09,766
RYOGA (VOICEOVER):
How can she love him

52
00:04:09,866 --> 00:04:12,500
when it's so obvious
he doesn't deserve her?

53
00:04:14,133 --> 00:04:16,966
