seen a pig, has you?

179
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,033
RYOGA: Why do you ask?

180
00:10:15,133 --> 00:10:17,266
-You didn't go in
at it, did you?

181
00:10:17,366 --> 00:10:19,366
-Are you saying that
I'd eat my own friend?

182
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,333
I'd, uh, kind of
like to go to bed

183
00:10:22,433 --> 00:10:23,566
now, so if you wouldn't mind--

184
00:10:25,066 --> 00:10:28,366
MAN 1: Dang, could have sworn
that little runt was in there.

185
00:10:28,466 --> 00:10:30,200
MAN 2: Maybe it done run away.

186
