MAN 3: Of course it
ran away, you moron.

187
00:10:32,466 --> 00:10:34,633
Didn't we just say runaway pig?

188
00:10:34,733 --> 00:10:37,566
-[squealing]

189
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,366
-Close call, huh?

190
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:45,100
Whoa, hey, cut it out.

191
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,066
What are you doing?

192
00:10:46,166 --> 00:10:48,266
I'm saving my first
kiss for Akane.

193
00:10:48,366 --> 00:10:52,533
I didn't just say what
I think I said, did I?

194
00:10:54,433 --> 00:10:54,874
Oh, Akane!

195
00:10:56,466 --> 00:10:58,133
-Come back here,
you little runt.

196
00:10:58,233 --> 00:11:00,533
