perfect complexion.

199
00:11:04,366 --> 00:11:05,100
-Ranma!

200
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,333
What do you think you're doing?

201
00:11:06,433 --> 00:11:08,000
-Oh, you little coward.

202
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:10,366
